title: City Home Chemical Collection Date Set For Oct. 24 (City of Irving, TX)
text: ( Source : City of Irving, TX ) Solid Waste Services is making it even easier for residents to dispose of household chemicals by offering a home chemical waste collection from 9 a.m. to 1 p.m. Oct. 24 at 128 N. Briery Road . Items accepted
